Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:12.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Pier 13\NGarbage Collection Site\NAuthorized Personnel Only
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an awfully ugly robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to fight in earnest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't meet my end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:48.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:52.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:56.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:58.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:00.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:04.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:08.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's like this enormous suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here begins a story of science \Nfiction and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:36.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:36.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:40.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:40.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:59.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:59.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:05.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:05.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:17.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:17.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:24.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:24.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Big Bother, Even for Peter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the butler \Nuniform just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's settled! Metamorphosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that can wait for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, you have plans for \Nme to cross-dress again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the ratings, it \Nmay get slotted in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that aside, for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking you can't be dressed \Nlike that for the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it. You're \Ngoing to change clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I can... I can change on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That looks quite good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I'm capable of \Nchanging on my own, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressed like that, somehow it makes \Nyou actually look like a boy your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're off, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nagi, your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss, will you be okay \Ngoing to an amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that you're a \Nbit of a social recluse, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't refer to me like I'm at the \Nforefront of some modern disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you don't like going out and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I would bother to go \Nout to the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is within the bounds of the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Mi... Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, Michael Jackson's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? We didn't need to actually go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the luxury that the Sanzenin \Nfamily commands certainly is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one at Isumi's \Nplace and at Saku's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you ladies doing, getting \Nthem like it's a PS3 or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why this sudden visit \Nto the amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's because, you know, \Nduring the seaside camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to have much fun with \Nyou because of how things were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, summer break's almost over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I-I want to enjoy it as much \Nas possible, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no, so... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think an empty amusement \Npark feels a bit sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look, look! Friends of the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a new friend \Nvisiting us today, nyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to have \Nsome mascot characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Little Kik Punch, a forest \Nfairy of NagiNagiLand, nyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not a nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we haven't had a \Nvisitor in so long, nyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Seriously, thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, thank you, nyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I just heard his true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Incidentally, when was the \Nlast time you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, about 3 years ago, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, but 3 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be tough for \Nthe people on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no "people on the inside"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but you're wearing stuffed suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said there aren't and I meant it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fairies of the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, fairies, nyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids! Here we go with \Nthe NagiNagi workout!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Get over here quick
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}I'm a bit mad
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Get over here quick
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you have such a grand \Namusement park at your residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}At mach speeds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old geezer gave it to me \Na while back for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old geezer? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I recall correctly, I've met him, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But so it was a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess your grandfather \Nis quite kind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, look carefully around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:41.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, all the rides \Nat this amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...require that you're over 140cm tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:46.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be at least 140cm tall to ride
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}140cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}140! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, almost none of \Nthe rides are available to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a horribly elaborate \Nway to pick on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inconceivable that he would do \Nanything that might make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss is as tiny as \Never and can't ride them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but {\i1}you{\i0} can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come on over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got our first visitor \Never to ride the attractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if possible, I'd like \Nsomething safer next...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, the horror house might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horror house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. That won't have a \Nheight requirement, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, wh-wh-what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Horror houses are... s-s-scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what they're for, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No, I'm not scared! I'll \Nhave you know, I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be dangerous if there's a \Nhole in the floor or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. At this rate, they're \Ngoing to bypass the horror house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we've practiced so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're not careful and we \Nmake the Miss cry or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check first to see if \Nthere's anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entering the horror house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can friggin' roll him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're going to friggin' roll him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, the degree of \Nperfection here is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might make the Miss cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll kill me before it scares me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the back of the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That weapon doesn't have a back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given this situation, maybe \NI'll be permitted to use {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure to get permission for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest technique of Dragon Shiryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're too optimistic, my dearie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, still didn't happen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to make this \Nlook like an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're clearly out for blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... You want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say, I suppose it's \Na direct grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't remember me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I have no idea who you might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what grudge do you have against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard! Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you can see me in this dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get close to you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how well you hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! We turned the lights on, \Nso you won't be scared, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This isn't scary now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who he is or where \Nhe's from, but he's one ugly robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stinking brat! You, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! You're new here! The hell \Nare you doing going after the Miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow! Owowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}O-Ouch! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us! Don't \Nunderestimate the forest fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debt-ridden butler, just you remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get even with you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your precious summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the amusement \Npark to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a single customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This break was a good opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I might get to see \NHayate if I worked here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, hurry, hurry! We're going \Non the merry-go-round next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:25.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love is about passing each other by. \NTo be continued in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a group of four!\N({\u1}To{\u0}u-tou yonin gu{\u1}mi{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What animal has long ears?\N({\u1}Mi{\u0}mi no nagai doubutsu nan{\u1}da{\u0}?)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado Hyper Energy\NFujisusono Training Grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we will hereby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...commence the test for the \Nnew caregiver robot, Model 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contacts! Activate Model 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Caregiver Missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All missiles found their targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Fire Caregiver Laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Caregiver Goldion Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:28.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A sink or swim moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please wait a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The aging population will \Nhave nothing to fear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, something moving at high \Nspeeds is approaching Model 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too small. I can't verify the data!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Model 9, intercept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boost, on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Model 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the control chip's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin... Spin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin, spin, spin, spin, spin, spin, \Nspin, spin, spin, spin, spin, spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That debt-ridden butler's \Nno match for me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose industrial spy are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Makimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that even \Nyou've forgotten about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen that \Nrobot somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all! Miss Makimura, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... Without fail, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, I really, really had fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like Hayate went all-out, \Nwhoosh, and hopping with a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate really enjoyed it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes one happy when one does nice \Nthings for others, doesn't it, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made yourself very clear, \Nso please go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if Hayate is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I treated him for everything \Nin general, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've burnt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Into pure white ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can friggin' roll him now, \Nin one fell swoop and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're the robot from earlier today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you showed up in Episode 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the caregiver robot, who \Nwas defeated by Hayate. Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You recognize me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, why are you the \Nonly one who remembered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, unlike you, sitting on \Nyour laurels as the protagonist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've watched the opening \Nsequence to death every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because it's the only place \Nwhere I show up on a regular basis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this Eight's in a similar situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets no screen time, but he \Nshows up in the opening sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Was this robot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We haven't seen the "very generous \Npeople" next to him lately, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm going to get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound effects are quite thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What could this commotion be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it to Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been on a roll today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all your fault for going on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Because I was defeated by you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, you're going to become the \Nbest caregiver robot in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my creator's expectations \Nriding solely on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent day and night undergoing experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was boring, but I did my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:07.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Developer\NShiori Makimura 22yrs (single)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I had her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's from "Beet the Vandel Buster".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Eight was defeated \Nby some scummy human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was defeated like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my Caregiver Missiles didn't even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll cancel the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea that we should have robots \Ndo everything is wrong to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, its design and functionality \Nare both super lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I lost everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I ended up being disposed \Nof as nonburnable trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spacey and forgetful, the Chief \Ncompletely forgot about me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems she's been devoting herself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to developing a new caregiver robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my... my pain will not be assuaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to recapture her smile \Nagain and to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I have to beat you and that \Nstupid pigtail girl to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! You're just a pet, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Scrap Sandayuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler-in-debt's a scummy human, \Nwho's pitiful and boneheaded,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't care how much \Nyou friggin' roll him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone who harms the Miss \Nwill have to answer to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, the Miss is spoiled, \Nwillful, and domineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She acts on impulse and she \Nnever admits to being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's twice as stubborn as others, \Nignorant of the world, and haughty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, her weakness is that she \Ncan't sleep alone in a darkened room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while she insists that \Nshe has athletic ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she actually doesn't, which all \Nmakes her a worthless person...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, she's the person I owe my life to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't really know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like something was \Nsaid that really pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyone who turns against the Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! Wh-Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was out to kill you and \Nyou're going to protect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how lonely and sad \Nit feels to be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we had someone who \Ntook us in and saved us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that goes for you, too, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've experienced something similar, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand how I feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, let me friggin' roll \Nyou, right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound is growing louder again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to security's report,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that caregiver robot from \Nearlier has come for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems to be going on a huge rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you sure we don't need to go help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Hayate would lose against \Nsomeone he's fought before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's Version 8.1 now and \Nit seems to have powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8.1? That's just a patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Hayate is fighting for me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sort of warms your heart, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just hope he's not getting burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My new lethal mode that \Ncame with the upgrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito Destroy Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Japanese summer is \Nfilled with mosquitoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:32.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To ensure one's owner sleeps comfortably,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this functionality is a must.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why don't we stop right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to win \Nagainst us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes, I \Nwill once again get her to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That voice... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, thank goodness, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I remembered you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So? What are you doing \Nhere after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already abandoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a little mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw you out as nonburnable \Ntrash without even thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really feel bad about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, you're not nonburnable trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what a tearjerker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're oversized trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. We spoke on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of the Consumer \NElectronics Recycling Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you're not allowed to just \Nthrow electronic appliances away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The workers will disassemble \Nyou properly to dispose of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it. Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad it was the Miss who found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this ends on a far too dismal note!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we have to save Eight somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what can we possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Is this Makimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. You must not heartlessly \Ndestroy that junky robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I had no idea you \Nhad such a special talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use stuff like Kamehameha \Nto defeat your opponent yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't quite gotten that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:38.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally, shortly after \Nleaving the residence, Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Makimura, please go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:46.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, it seems he's \Nmoved on to a new phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:49.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, in pursuit of the throne \Nof victory in the Fishlympics,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:52.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they will fight the guardian of the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:22:01.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:22:01.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:09.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:09.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:35.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:58.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:58.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:10.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:10.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, it'll \Nbe clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Isumi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, Isumi wasn't able \Nto say anything about the song,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this time, I'm here to back her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Isumi, this song is, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got your sort of dreamy feel, \Nand a laid-back, mellow feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plus this "boof" feel, so I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:50.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid that does not get \Nthe message across at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, well, you know, it's a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.59,0:23:59.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we're fishing! \NWe're going to fish up tons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll do fly fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:19.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly fishing? Aren't we starting \Nwith something far too advanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:06.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanpei in "Fishing Lover Sanpei" \Nwas catching tons with fly fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sanpei could do it, \Nthere's no way I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:12.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it's not good to get \Nmanga and reality mixed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:15.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one! I got one! I got one! Yaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:16.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:19.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Wonder Who Came Up with the Sound \NEffect 'Kapooon'. It's Awesome".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:21.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that the \Nmoment we were left alone,
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.91,0:24:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wonder Who Came Up with the Sound \NEffect 'Kapooon'. It's Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,that Hayate would sidle up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:25.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The fun will be in the \Nred zone again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.37,0:24:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
